data.value: Hyundai Creta is a 5 seater SUV car in a price range of Rs. 10.99 Lakh to 20.14 Lakh in India. Creta is offered with 1.5L diesel engine and 1.5L petrol engines in both manual and automatic transmission. Hyundai Creta gives a mileage of 17.4 Kmpl on petrol and 21.8 Kmpl on diesel. It is available in 28 variants and 7 beautiful colours. Considering the price and specs the Creta is a tough competition to Honda Elevate, Kia Seltos and Maruti Brezza.
